name: Incubate
tagline: Salesforce FAQ that you must know
body:
### Welcome to Project Incubate.
This is open source community driven page designed to offer answers to common question you seek while hiring Salesforce Developers around the globe. Our motives is to share knowledge and we recommend highly referring Salesforce Documents and resources for all references.

### Authors and Contributors
At the moment it is solely driven by Harshit @mailtoharshit, but open for contribution from public.

### Support or Contact
